-- Masdar Plans to Increase Clean-Tech Fund to $400 Million From $255 Million
-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 2010-10-20T09:52:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/masdar-plans-to-increase-clean-tech-fund-to-400-million-from-255-million.html
Masdar, the Abu Dhabi government-
backed renewable energy company, plans to increase the size of
its clean-tech fund to $400 million by the end of this year from
$265 million, Chief Executive Officer Sultan al-Jaber said at a
conference in London today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in Abu Dhabi at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
